title: Bug 123036: Data in a report is doubly stored
description: Currently, we are experiencing an issue where data in a report is being stored twice.
OB: The data in the report is being duplicated in the storage system, causing unnecessary redundancy.
EB: The bug causes data duplication in the report, resulting in excessive storage usage and potential data inconsistency.
SR: Investigate the source of the duplication issue and fix it to prevent unnecessary data redundancy in the report.
